te3 chiong ou5-tho5 lai5 siuN2-su3 hiah-e5 kho2-lin5 e5 song3-hiong lang5, lai5 ki5-to2, chiu7 Siong7-te3 e7 hou7 chit8-liap8 ou5-tho5 chau2-chhut li2 sou2 ai3 e5 ou5-tho5-a2.¡¨ Sin3-kiat thiaN-liau2 chin kam2-kek. 
  Theh8 hit liap8 tho5-a2 beh chhut-khi3 goa7-bin7 e5 si5, hun5-chhiok tui3 i kong2, ¡§Sin3-kiat hiaN, goa2 ia7 chiong chit8 ki ¡¥chhau2-tek8¡¦ hou7 li2, chit-e5 chhau2-tek8, bo5-lun7 sim2-mih8 lang5 pun5, thiN-tiong e5 poe-chiau2 long2 e7 poe lai5 kap li2 cho3 peng5-iu2. Hian7-chai7 siuN7 ai3 pun5, chong2-si7 chhiu7-na5 lai7 e5 chiau2-lui7 long2 teh khun3, na7 ka7 in phah-chhiN2 chin phaiN2-se3. TaN chit-ki hou7 li2, na7 bo5 phoaN7 e5 si5 li2 thang pun5, na7 beh khou ke-a2 lai5, pun5 ia7 chin ho2 eng7.¡¨ Sin3-kiat toa7 ka7 i seh to-sia7. Chit si5 sian5 eng7 chhou-chhou ke7-ke e5 siaN tui3 i kong2 ¡§Sin3-kiat hiaN, goa2 m7 chai sim2-mih8 si5 chiah e7 koh tu2-tioh8 li2, sou2-i2 ai3 chiong ¡¥sian5 e5 sit8-a2¡¦ hou7 li2, li2 na7 koa3 ti7 seng-khu, chiu7 e7-thang chhin-chhiuN7 goan2 an2-ni ti7 khong-tiong chu7-iu5 lai5 poe¡¨. I kong2 an2-ni chiu7 poe2 thou5, tui3 thou5-te2 theh8 sian5 e5 khak hou7 i kong2 ¡§Che tioh8 ti7 beh pang-chan7 lang5 e5 si5 chiah thang eng7, na7 siuN7 ai3 than3 chiN5, a2-si7 hou7 lang5 o-lo2 chiu7 bo5 hau7, chhiaN2 li2 e7 ki3-tit.¡¨ Sin3-kiat theh8 chit 3 hang7 po2-poe3 tui3 tong7-hiat8 chhut-lai5 e5 si5, niau-a2 A-giok8 chau2 lai5 ka7 i seh-sia7 kong2, ¡§Sin3-kiat hiaN, chin ku2 siu7 li2 e5 chiau3-kou3 chin to-sia7, goa2 chiam7-si5 e7 kap toa7-him5 in cho3-hoe2 toa3, chhiaN2 m7 bian2 khoa3-lu7.¡¨ 
