  ¡§Pa-pa, goa2 the3 li2, li2 seng khi3 khun3.¡¨ Iu2-hau3 e5 Sin3-kiat kong2 an2-ni chiu7 tui3 pa-pa e5 chhiu2 chiap teng-hoe2. Bo5 joa7 ku2 choe3 am3 e5 chhia chiu7 koe3-khi3. ¡§TaN, tioh8 khai-si2 lai5 cho3, chhu3-piN, thih-lou7-piN, kim-am3 long2 lai5 ka7 i cheng3 ou5-tho5-a2, bin5-a2 cha2-khi2 hou7 pa-pa tioh8-kiaN chit8-e7¡¨. I siuN7 an2-ni chiu7 tui3 te7-a2 te2 theh8 ou5-tho5-a2 chhut-lai5, chiau3 toa7-him5 sou2 kong2, liam7 Chu2 e5 ki5-to2-bun5, chiu7 tit8-tit8 haiN3. ¡§Khok, khok......¡¨, tho5-a2-chi2 tit8-tit8 lin3 chhut-lai5, Sin3-kiat chiu7 chiong hiah-e5 cheng3 ti7 chhu3 e5 si3-piN, kap thih-lou7 e5 nng7-peng5, chin ki5-biau7, chit8-e7 cheng3 loh8-khi3, sui5-si5 puh-ge5, piN3-cho3 chhiu7 tit8-tit8 toa7 chang5, koh kiat chin che7 koe2-chi2, hou7 Sin3-kiat tioh8 chit8-kiaN. 
